graph TD
    Client[Streamlit Frontend] --> API[FastAPI Backend]
    API --> Graph[LangGraph Workflow]

    Graph --> Commercial[상권분석 Agent]
    Graph --> Population[유동인구 Agent]
    Graph --> Demographics[인구통계 Agent]
    Graph --> Cost[비용산정 Agent]
    Graph --> Competition[경쟁분석 Agent]
    Graph --> Trend[트렌드 Agent]
    Graph --> Legal[법규검토 Agent]
    Graph --> Supervisor[Supervisor]
    Graph --> Report[리포트 Agent]

    Commercial --> SEMAS[소상공인 API]
    Commercial --> Golmok[우리마을가게 API]
    Population --> Seoul[서울 열린데이터]
    Demographics --> SGIS[통계청 SGIS]
    Cost --> MOLIT[국토교통부 API]
    Competition --> SEMAS
    Legal --> VectorDB[ChromaDB / RAG]
    Trend --> SNS[SNS 크롤링]

    Supervisor -->|재분석| Commercial
    Supervisor -->|완료| Report

    Report --> PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL)]
    API --> Redis[(Redis Cache)]
